@singaporeinsiders Amazing photo of @dotzsoh!!! Congratulations @dotzsoh! Great photo! 😍👍
In need of a staycay now! 😭

I was fortunate to work in Singapore 2005-2007. I even had a green card. Been there 11 times. I really miss the hawker centers, Clarke Quay and having a Tiger beer at Handlebar on 10 Lock Road. Hope to go back next year for a long visit. Stay safe!
